            . I live with Mr. Morris, a pawnbroker, of York-street, Westminster. On the 1st of June a shirt was pawned in the name of Pearce, for 4s.</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270111-106-person1071">
                  JOHN 
                  WARREN
