                     <interp inst="t18270111-106-person1071" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took the prisoner in charge on the 2d of June, and found the duplicate of the watch upon him. The prosecutor was then at sea.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. Two men came on board and eat, and then took me ashore - one of them gave me the watch.</p>
               <p>
